## Agent Conventions

- Prefer modular `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` over duplicating code in rules.
- `globs` syntax: comma-separated, no spaces after commas, no quotes.
- File size target: 200–700 lines; split when exceeded.
- Before architectural changes: read `@docs/PRD.md`.
- CodeGraph + Graphify: structural code via CodeGraph MCP (`@codegraph.mdc`); macro architecture via `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` — `@docs/CODEGRAPH.md`, `@docs/GRAPHIFY.md`, `@105-graphify-solo-dev.mdc`. No `graphify watch` on low-end hardware. `.codegraph/` is local-only (gitignored).
